set element flexibally in a row.

list of property which is only effected while apply flex.
(1) flex-grow (child element)
(2) flex-shrink (child element)
(3) flex-basis (child element)
(4) flex (child element)
(5) flex-direction 
(6) flex-wrap 
(7) flex-flow 
(9) justify-content 
(10) align-items 
(11) align-content 
(12) align-self (child element)
(13) gap (row-gap, column-gap)

justify => word => effect horizontally 
align => word => effect vertically 